\
We have decided to add a new feature to the EXCLUSIVE keyword.\
\
Before you would have to list out all of the directories that were exclusive\
\
EXCLUSIVE paramesh UG\
\
Now that Simulations are treated as full Units in Flash3 we wanted to make sure that only one Simulation got included in a problem\
\
but writing out\
\
EXCLUSIVE Sod Sedov Advect ShockCyl ..... \
\
would be too long, especially if someone wanted to add a new Simulation.\
\
So we have made new functionality\
EXCLUSIVE *\
\
This means only one directory can be chosen.  It is the same as listing off all of the directories where the Config is found and this is in fact what the python script does.  It's just short hand notation}